<plot>Barney is a washed up boxer looking for one last fight. He has let his life fall to pieces. His wife and daughter have left him and he can only find solace in a bottle of booze. As the shards of his past come streaming back in this disjointed tale, the burden that he carries soon comes to light. As a one-time champion, Barney killed a young fighter in the ring! Now, he decides to go back to his old trainer Telly to get in shape for one last fight. Can he find peace? Can he find salvation? At least he knows he will "go out in a blaze of glory."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?134042</url></doc>
